7/8. While the cards look favourable for France in the European Tug of war, the OHL Dunkirk affair resurfaces, forcing Laugier and Rickwaert to navigate troubled waters between diplomacy and foul play.

8/8. After an incriminating court document is released and the media get hold of it, Rickwaert will risk anything to save his own back...
